Use: Flip to the next section.

Equip: Every 5 sec spent in combat sacrifices 7,105 of your health to gain 1,493 Intellect. This effect can stack up to 3 times and lasts until combat ends.

Equip: Gain Ascendance every 8 seconds spent in combat.

Ascendance grants 89 of a random secondary stat for 15 sec, stacking up to 10 times.

This is a Nerubian embellishment.
